    <h1>Rank Tracking</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of monitoring where your website's pages appear in search results for specific keywords over time. Without rank tracking, you're running an SEO programme blind — you can't optimise what you don't measure.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
